      <caption>
        <title>The distribution of genetic differentiation between and diversity within two different geographical <italic>Liriodendron</italic> groups along 19 chromosomes</title>
        <p>Distributions of genetic differentiation (Fst) between western and eastern China groups and nucleotide diversity (p) among accessions came from western and eastern China are plotted. The genetic differentiation between and nucleotide diversity within two groups are all calculated in a 2-Mb sliding window with a 1-Mb step. The genetic differentiation distribution is mapped on idiograms while genetic diversity distributions are mapped along the idiograms as line charts (a) and area charts (b).</p>
      </caption>
